- There are no observable code-level regressions tied to application logic, auth, or API behavior in this diff.
- The current working diff is dominated by environment-generated/local runtime artifacts (`.local/share/pnpm/store`, `.local/state/workflow-logs`, and large deletions under `cortes/.next`). These are setup side effects, not durable project changes.

Security: none observed.

Next actions:
